{"work":"KJV + Strong's","code":"2Jo","book":"2 John","chapterCount":1,"chapters":[{"number":1,"verses":[{"id":"2Jo|1|1","reference":"2 John 1:1","number":1,"text":"The elder unto the elect lady and her children, whom I love in the truth; and not I only, but also all they that have known the truth;","strongs":[{"label":"The elder","strongsId":"G4245"},{"label":"unto the elect","strongsId":"G1588"},{"label":"lady","strongsId":"G2959"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"her","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"children","strongsId":"G5043"},{"label":"whom","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"I","strongsId":"G1473"},{"label":"love","strongsId":"G25"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"the truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"I","strongsId":"G1473"},{"label":"only","strongsId":"G3441"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"also","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"they that have known","strongsId":"G1097"},{"label":"the truth","strongsId":"G225"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|2","reference":"2 John 1:2","number":2,"text":"For the truth's sake, which dwelleth in us, and shall be with us for ever.","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"the truth's sake","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3588"},{"label":"dwelleth","strongsId":"G3306"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2254"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"shall be","strongsId":"G2071"},{"label":"with","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"ever","strongsId":"G165"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|3","reference":"2 John 1:3","number":3,"text":"Grace be with you, mercy, and peace, from God the Father, and from the Lord Jesus Christ, the Son of the Father, in truth and love.","strongs":[{"label":"Grace","strongsId":"G5485"},{"label":"be","strongsId":"G2071"},{"label":"with","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"you","strongsId":"G5216"},{"label":"mercy","strongsId":"G1656"},{"label":"and peace","strongsId":"G1515"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G3844"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"the Father","strongsId":"G3962"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G3844"},{"label":"the Lord","strongsId":"G2962"},{"label":"Jesus","strongsId":"G2424"},{"label":"Christ","strongsId":"G5547"},{"label":"the Son","strongsId":"G5207"},{"label":"of the Father","strongsId":"G3962"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"love","strongsId":"G26"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|4","reference":"2 John 1:4","number":4,"text":"I rejoiced greatly that I found of thy children walking in truth, as we have received a commandment from the Father.","strongs":[{"label":"I rejoiced","strongsId":"G5463"},{"label":"greatly","strongsId":"G3029"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G3754"},{"label":"I found","strongsId":"G2147"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"thy","strongsId":"G4675"},{"label":"children","strongsId":"G5043"},{"label":"walking","strongsId":"G4043"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"as","strongsId":"G2531"},{"label":"we have received","strongsId":"G2983"},{"label":"a commandment","strongsId":"G1785"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G3844"},{"label":"the Father","strongsId":"G3962"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|5","reference":"2 John 1:5","number":5,"text":"And now I beseech thee, lady, not as though I wrote a new commandment unto thee, but that which we had from the beginning, that we love one another.","strongs":[{"label":"And","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"now","strongsId":"G3568"},{"label":"I beseech","strongsId":"G2065"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"lady","strongsId":"G2959"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"as though","strongsId":"G5613"},{"label":"I wrote","strongsId":"G1125"},{"label":"I wrote","strongsId":"G1125"},{"label":"a new","strongsId":"G2537"},{"label":"commandment","strongsId":"G1785"},{"label":"unto thee","strongsId":"G4671"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"that which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"we had","strongsId":"G2192"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G575"},{"label":"the beginning","strongsId":"G746"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"we love","strongsId":"G25"},{"label":"one another","strongsId":"G240"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|6","reference":"2 John 1:6","number":6,"text":"And this is love, that we walk after his commandments. This is the commandment, That, as ye have heard from the beginning, ye should walk in it.","strongs":[{"label":"And","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"this","strongsId":"G3778"},{"label":"is","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"love","strongsId":"G26"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"we walk","strongsId":"G4043"},{"label":"after","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"commandments","strongsId":"G1785"},{"label":"This","strongsId":"G3778"},{"label":"is","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"the commandment","strongsId":"G1785"},{"label":"That","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"as","strongsId":"G2531"},{"label":"ye have heard","strongsId":"G191"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G575"},{"label":"the beginning","strongsId":"G746"},{"label":"ye should walk","strongsId":"G4043"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"it","strongsId":"G846"}]},{"id":"2Jo|1|7","reference":"2 John 1:7","number":7,"text":"For many deceivers are entered into the world, who confess not that Jesus Christ is come in the flesh. This is a deceiver and an antichrist.","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G3754"},{"label":"many","strongsId":"G4183"},{"label":"deceivers","strongsId":"G4108"},{"label":"are entered","strongsId":"G1525"},{"label":"into","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"the world","strongsId":"G2889"},{"label":"who","strongsId":"G3588"},{"label":"confess","strongsId":"G3670"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"